31
00:03:49,300 --> 00:03:51,433
- Brandon: YES, SIR.
- Harry: THANK YOU SIR.

32
00:03:51,500 --> 00:03:53,466
- Bear: SID!
- HUH?

33
00:03:53,533 --> 00:03:56,900
- IS THAT...
BEAR, BEAR WALKEN!

34
00:03:56,966 --> 00:03:58,433
- SID GALARDE!

35
00:03:58,500 --> 00:04:00,366
- ( both laughing )

36
00:04:00,433 --> 00:04:02,866
- YOU LOOK A LOT OLDER
THAN THE LAST TIME WE MET

37
00:04:02,933 --> 00:04:05,966
YOU'VE GOT SO MANY NEW WRINKLES
I BARELY RECOGNIZED YOU.

38
00:04:06,033 --> 00:04:07,833
- THE SAME GOES FOR YOU!

39
00:04:07,900 --> 00:04:10,333
- Sherry: HI UNCLE SID,
IT'S NICE TO SEE YOU,

40
00:04:10,400 --> 00:04:14,966
- SHERRY! YOU GOT SO BIG!
GUESS WE HAVE GOTTEN OLD.

41
00:04:15,033 --> 00:04:16,466
- YES INDEED.

42
00:04:16,533 --> 00:04:19,066
- I'D LIKE MY SON TO
JOIN THE FAMILY TOO

43
00:04:19,133 --> 00:04:21,666
BUT HE GETS INTO TROUBLE
ALL THE TIME.

44
00:04:21,733 --> 00:04:24,566
I WISH HE WERE A LOT MORE
LIKE THESE TWO YOUNG MEN.

45
00:04:24,633 --> 00:04:26,366
- HAVE YOU TWO
INTRODUCED YOURSELVES?

46
00:04:26,433 --> 00:04:28,366
- YES, SIR. WE HAVE.

47
00:04:28,433 --> 00:04:31,966
- EXCUSE ME FATHER,
I HAVEN'T BEEN INTRODUCED YET.

48
00:04:32,033 --> 00:04:36,000
- YES DEAR, YOU'RE RIGHT.
LET ME INTRODUCE YOU.

49
00:04:36,066 --> 00:04:37,733
THIS IS MY DAUGHTER.

50
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:41,633
- HOW DO YOU DO?
MY NAME'S SHERRY WALKEN.

51
00:04:41,700 --> 00:04:44,133
- WELL HELLO THERE,
I'M A NEW MEMBER OF THE FAMILY.

52
00:04:44,200 --> 00:04:46,033
I'M HARRY MACDOWEL.

53
00:04:46,100 --> 00:04:47,600
- I'M BRANDON HEAT.

54
00:04:48,300 --> 00:04:49,266
- OH!

55
00:04:50,400 --> 00:04:52,333
- SOMETHING WRONG?
- OH!

56
