59
00:04:58,466 --> 00:05:02,700
IF YOU'D LIKE
WE COULD TASTE THEM TOGETHER.

60
00:05:06,300 --> 00:05:07,533
- I'D LOVE TO.

61
00:05:13,233 --> 00:05:15,900
- LOOKS LIKE YOUR PARTNER
IS A REAL LADIES MAN.

62
00:05:17,300 --> 00:05:18,900
- LET HARRY KNOW,

63
00:05:18,966 --> 00:05:21,500
THAT IF HE FOOLS WITH MY
DAUGHTER IN ANY WAY WHATSOEVER

64
00:05:21,566 --> 00:05:23,100
I'LL KILL HIM, UNDERSTAND?

65
00:05:23,166 --> 00:05:27,733
- I'LL TELL HIM SIR.
- A PROTECTIVE FATHER.

66
00:05:27,800 --> 00:05:29,366
- OH BEAR, SO THERE
YOU ARE,

67
00:05:29,433 --> 00:05:31,700
I'M GLAD YOU COULD
JOIN US TODAY.

68
00:05:31,766 --> 00:05:33,333
- SORRY I CAME SO LATE.

69
00:05:33,400 --> 00:05:36,600
I APOLOGIZE SIR. THERE WAS A
MINOR TERRITORIAL DISPUTE,

70
00:05:36,666 --> 00:05:37,833
BUT IT'S SETTLED NOW.

71
00:05:37,900 --> 00:05:39,900
- COME NOW,
I KNOW HOW BUSY YOU ARE.

72
00:05:39,966 --> 00:05:42,233
THERE'S NO NEED TO APOLOGIZE.

73
00:05:42,300 --> 00:05:45,066
- THANK YOU SIR.
- WELL, SID.

74
00:05:45,133 --> 00:05:47,100
I SEE YOU'VE ALREADY
MET MY NEW SON.

75
00:05:47,166 --> 00:05:49,700
PLEASE TAKE GOOD
CARE OF HIM FOR ME.

76
00:05:49,766 --> 00:05:53,700
- I CERTAINLY WILL,
BIG DADDY.

77
00:05:53,766 --> 00:05:55,400
- IT'S HARD TO BELIEVE
THAT THOSE YOUNGSTERS

78
00:05:55,466 --> 00:05:58,033
ARE ALREADY MEMBERS
OF THE FAMILY.

79
00:05:58,100 --> 00:06:00,500
BIG DADDY'S BEEN
IN CONTROL OF MILLENNION

80
00:06:00,566 --> 00:06:02,366
SINCE HE FOUNDED
IT 30 YEARS AGO.

81
00:06:02,433 --> 00:06:04,166
DOES HE HAVE A
SUCCESSOR IN MIND?

82
00:06:04,233 --> 00:06:07,233
- NOT YET, HE'S STILL YOUNG.
IT'S GONNA BE A WHILE.

83
00:06:07,300 --> 00:06:10,066
- YEAH, BUT THE BOSS
DOESN'T HAVE ANY CHILDREN.

84
00:06:10,133 --> 00:06:12,866
SO SINCE HE HAS NO NATURAL
HEIR, HE SHOULD DECIDE

85
00:06:12,933 --> 00:06:14,366
WHO IT'S GOING TO BE.

86
00:06:14,433 --> 00:06:16,733
- I KNOW OF VERY FEW MEN
WHO WOULD BE ABLE

87
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:19,633
TO TAKE HIS PLACE.

88
00:06:19,700 --> 00:06:21,400
- WELL, WHAT ABOUT YOU BEAR?

89
00:06:22,066 --> 00:06:23,266
- NOT ME.

90
00:06:29,400 --> 00:06:30,400
HMM.

91
00:06:36,566 --> 00:06:37,600
- ( door closing )

92
00:06:37,666 --> 00:06:38,300
WHAT'S UP?

93
00:06:38,366 --> 00:06:40,600
TWO MEN WERE ROBBED AND KILLED.

94
00:06:40,666 --> 00:06:42,800
IT HAPPENED IN MY TERRITORY.

95
00:06:42,866 --> 00:06:46,133
THE MONEY'S NO BIG DEAL BUT
ONE WAS A GUEST FROM ALGERIA.

96
00:06:46,200 --> 00:06:48,066
- HMM.

97
00:06:48,133 --> 00:06:50,633
- THE KILLER WILL HAVE TO BE
DEALT WITH AT ONCE.

98
00:06:50,700 --> 00:06:52,766
OR THE ORGANIZATION
WILL LOSE FACE.

99
00:06:52,833 --> 00:06:55,800
WHICH WILL MAKE BIG DADDY'S
JOB EVEN MORE DIFFICULT.

100
00:06:57,866 --> 00:06:59,833
- WELL, I GUESS IN THIS
BUSINESS THERE'S ALWAYS

101
00:06:59,900 --> 00:07:01,033
GONNA BE SOME
KIND OF TROUBLE

102
00:07:01,100 --> 00:07:02,633
BUT IT HAS TO BE DEALT WITH.

103
00:07:03,333 --> 00:07:04,800
- THAT'S WHY I'M HERE.

104
00:07:06,033 --> 00:07:08,233
- ( laughing ) YES,
EXACTLY RIGHT.

105
00:07:12,833 --> 00:07:14,033
- ( man groaning )

106
00:07:16,866 --> 00:07:20,266
- Balladbird: SO, HOW WAS YOUR
DEBUT AT THE FAMILY PARTY?

107
00:07:20,333 --> 00:07:22,433
- BIT NERVE-WRACKING
EVEN FOR ME.

108
00:07:22,500 --> 00:07:24,566
- IF YOU ASK ME,
IT'S NOT FAIR YOU

109
00:07:24,633 --> 00:07:26,466
AND BRANDON JOINING THE
FAMILY WITHOUT US.

110
00:07:26,533 --> 00:07:28,800
- YOU'LL GET IN.
JUST GIVE ME SOME TIME.

111
00:07:28,866 --> 00:07:31,033
ONCE I'VE GOT A LITTLE MORE
CLOUT IN THE FAMILY,

112
00:07:31,100 --> 00:07:33,000
I CAN RECOMMEND YOU
GUYS TO MY BOSS.

113
00:07:33,066 --> 00:07:35,100
WERE COUNTING ON YOU HARRY.

114
00:07:35,166 --> 00:07:37,133
- OF COURSE. 'CAUSE
I'M NOT STOPPING

115
00:07:37,200 --> 00:07:38,800
TILL I GET WHERE
I WANNA GO.

116
00:07:38,866 --> 00:07:41,833
THIS IS THE LIST
OF EVERYONE IN THE FAMILY, BOB.

117
00:07:41,900 --> 00:07:44,833
FIND OUT EVERYTHING YOU CAN
ABOUT THEM, BUT DO IT SECRETLY.

118
00:07:44,900 --> 00:07:47,100
- Bob: I GOT YOU, HARRY.

119
00:07:47,166 --> 00:07:48,133
- THEY CLAIM TO BELIEVE

120
00:07:48,200 --> 00:07:50,766
IN THE CODE OF IRON
BUT IT'S A BIG FAMILY.

121
00:07:50,833 --> 00:07:53,366
I'M SURE THERE ARE
SKELETONS HIDDEN SOMEWHERE.

122
00:07:53,433 --> 00:07:55,966
- WOW, YOU'RE KIND OF SCARY.

123
00:07:56,033 --> 00:07:57,933
- I GOTTA FIND OUT
IF ANY OF THEM ARE TRAITORS

124
00:07:58,000 --> 00:07:59,566
FOR THE SAKE OF THE FAMILY.

125
00:07:59,633 --> 00:08:01,733
AND FOR MY SAKE AS WELL.

126
00:08:13,100 --> 00:08:14,100
- AH!

127
00:08:15,133 --> 00:08:16,133
( sighing )

128
00:08:17,633 --> 00:08:19,133
- Brandon: HOW'S IT GOING?

129
00:08:19,200 --> 00:08:21,166
- OH, HEY BRO.

130
00:08:22,266 --> 00:08:24,533
THANKS A LOT.
MAN, ARE YOU QUIET.

131
00:08:24,600 --> 00:08:27,233
- I DIDN'T EVEN KNOW
YOU'D COME IN.

132
00:08:27,300 --> 00:08:29,366
- SO SEEN THE TARGET?

133
00:08:29,433 --> 00:08:31,433
- NOT YET.
THE CURTAINS ARE CLOSED,

134
00:08:31,500 --> 00:08:33,566
AND THE LIGHTS ARE TURNED OFF.

135
00:08:35,000 --> 00:08:36,533
- HE'S THERE.
- HUH?

136
00:08:46,466 --> 00:08:47,700
- I'LL GO CHECK IT OUT.

137
00:08:56,400 --> 00:08:58,633
- IS THIS GUY A MONSTER OR WHAT?

138
00:08:59,800 --> 00:09:01,666
- Brandon: IT'S TAKEN CARE OF.

139
00:09:01,733 --> 00:09:04,200
- I SEE, GOOD WORK YOU TWO.

140
00:09:04,266 --> 00:09:06,366
I'LL CONTACT YOU
SHORTLY. LOOKS LIKE

141
00:09:06,433 --> 00:09:08,100
I'LL NEED ANOTHER FAVOR.

142
00:09:08,166 --> 00:09:10,633
- ANYTIME SIR.
- Bunji: EXCUSE US.

143
00:09:15,100 --> 00:09:19,033
- HEY, I'M SORRY.
RELAX, I WAS JUST TESTING YOU.

144
00:09:19,100 --> 00:09:20,500
- THEY BEAT YOU SID.

145
00:09:21,600 --> 00:09:24,033
- DID YOU TRAIN THEM?
- YEAH.

146
00:09:24,100 --> 00:09:26,100
- NO WONDER. LOOKS LIKE
BRANDON HERE TURNED OUT

147
00:09:26,166 --> 00:09:27,866
TO BE ONE HELL OF A GOOD STUDENT

148
00:09:27,933 --> 00:09:31,300
- HIS FRIEND HERE DID TOO.
- BUNJI KUGASHIRA SIR.

149
00:09:31,366 --> 00:09:32,733
- I'LL REMEMBER THAT.

150
00:09:32,800 --> 00:09:35,066
COME ON HAVE A DRINK WITH US.
YOU DO LIKE TO DRINK,

151
00:09:35,133 --> 00:09:36,933
- DON'T YOU? 
- SURE.

152
00:09:37,000 --> 00:09:40,900
- ( Sid laughing )

153
00:09:40,966 --> 00:09:43,066
- BEAR AND I HAD JUST
JOINED THE MAFIA

154
00:09:43,133 --> 00:09:45,066
WE WERE FIGHTING EACH OTHER
TOOTH AND NAIL TRYING

155
00:09:45,133 --> 00:09:47,133
TO GRAB MORE TERRITORY.

156
00:09:47,200 --> 00:09:49,366
AND NEITHER ONE OF US
WOULD GIVE AN INCH

157
00:09:49,433 --> 00:09:52,466
SO STUPID AND STUBBORN,
WE ALMOST SHOT EACH OTHER.

158
00:09:52,533 --> 00:09:55,300
AND WE PROBABLY WOULD HAVE
IF BIG DADDY HADN'T SHOWN UP

159
00:09:55,366 --> 00:09:58,000
AND OFFERED TO
MEDIATE OUR DISPUTE.

160
00:09:58,066 --> 00:10:00,200
TELL YOU THE TRUTH
THE WAY I SEE IT

161
00:10:00,266 --> 00:10:02,666
IF IT HADN'T BEEN FOR BIG DADDY,
ONE OF US WOULD HAVE ENDED

162
00:10:02,733 --> 00:10:04,600
UP IN THE NEXT WORLD FOR SURE.

163
00:10:04,666 --> 00:10:08,100
- ONE OF US, MEANING YOU!
- IS THAT SO?

164
00:10:09,333 --> 00:10:11,700
( laughing ) NO DOUBT ABOUT IT.

165
00:10:11,766 --> 00:10:13,433
IN THOSE DAYS YOU
WERE STRONG AS

166
00:10:13,500 --> 00:10:15,400
A DEVIL AND TWICE AS ARMORY.

167
00:10:15,466 --> 00:10:17,666
- BUT YOU WERE
A LOT MORE POPULAR.

168
00:10:17,733 --> 00:10:22,633
- YEAH RIGHT, ABSOLUTELY RIGHT.
EVERYONE LIKES SID GALARDE.

169
00:10:23,666 --> 00:10:25,900
COME ON, HAVE ANOTHER DRINK.

170
00:10:25,966 --> 00:10:28,200
- THANK YOU, I HAVE ONE, SIR.

171
00:10:28,266 --> 00:10:30,800
- LOTS MORE WHERE THAT
CAME FROM, RIGHT?

172
00:10:35,633 --> 00:10:37,200
- Bunji: HEY BRO...

173
00:10:37,266 --> 00:10:40,100
TELL ME, ARE THOSE GUYS
WHAT YOU CALL FAMILY?

174
00:10:41,666 --> 00:10:43,733
YOU SEE, I'M AN ORPHAN.

175
00:10:43,800 --> 00:10:45,466
SO I DON'T REALLY KNOW
WHAT A FAMILY IS,

176
00:10:45,533 --> 00:10:49,033
YOU KNOW WHAT I MEAN?

177
00:10:49,100 --> 00:10:50,600
- NEITHER DO I.

178
00:10:55,466 --> 00:10:57,633
- WHAT'S THE MATTER?
YOU'RE NOT THE TYPE

179
00:10:57,700 --> 00:10:58,966
TO GET THIS DRUNK.

180
00:10:59,033 --> 00:11:00,766
WHAT'S UP SID?

181
00:11:00,833 --> 00:11:02,733
- I SUPPOSE I JUST
GOT CARRIED AWAY,

182
00:11:02,800 --> 00:11:05,866
REMEMBERING HOW
THINGS USED TO BE.

183
00:11:05,933 --> 00:11:09,966
- YOU'RE GETTING OLD, SID.
- OH YEAH? LOOK WHO'S TALKING.

184
00:11:12,533 --> 00:11:15,200
HEY, BEAR...

185
00:11:16,500 --> 00:11:19,533
GREAT BEING YOUNG
LIKE THOSE TWO ARE.

186
00:11:19,600 --> 00:11:23,766
JUST STARTING UP THE LADDER AND
LOOKING FORWARD TO THE FUTURE.

187
00:11:23,833 --> 00:11:27,033
- BUT YOUNGSTERS DO
STUPID THINGS SOMETIMES.

188
00:11:29,300 --> 00:11:32,700
- YEAH, THEY DO. DON'T THEY?

189
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:37,600
YOU'RE ABSOLUTELY RIGHT...

190
00:11:43,433 --> 00:11:46,233
- IT'S HARRY MACDOWEL.

191
00:11:46,300 --> 00:11:48,066
DO YOU KNOW IF BIG
DADDY READ THE MATERIAL

192
00:11:48,133 --> 00:11:51,466
I SENT IN THE OTHER DAY?

193
00:11:51,533 --> 00:11:52,866
I UNDERSTAND.

194
00:11:53,933 --> 00:11:56,433
YEAH, IT WAS PRETTY UNSETTLING.

195
00:11:56,500 --> 00:11:59,666
BUT I KNEW I HAD TO SEND IT
IN ORDER TO PROTECT THE FAMILY.

196
00:11:59,733 --> 00:12:01,333
YES, SIR. WHEN YOU
SEE BIG DADDY,

197
00:12:01,400 --> 00:12:03,966
WOULD YOU PLEASE
GIVE HIM MY BEST?

198
00:12:04,033 --> 00:12:06,400
RIGHT, THANK YOU VERY MUCH.

199
00:12:08,733 --> 00:12:10,233
- Sherry: SORRY TO
KEEP YOU WAITING.

200
00:12:10,300 --> 00:12:13,466
- THAT'S OKAY,
I JUST GOT HERE MYSELF.

201
00:12:13,533 --> 00:12:16,266
THAT'S A BEAUTIFUL DRESS,
YOU LOOK GREAT!

202
00:12:16,333 --> 00:12:19,600
- THANK YOU, MR. MACDOWEL.

203
00:12:19,666 --> 00:12:21,533
- PLEASE, CALL ME HARRY.

204
00:12:21,600 --> 00:12:23,866
- ( gasping ) OH!

205
00:13:04,233 --> 00:13:05,466
- PRETTY SWEET!

206
00:13:05,533 --> 00:13:07,500
- ( phone ringing )

207
00:13:08,900 --> 00:13:09,900
- HELLO?

208
00:13:11,466 --> 00:13:12,600
IT'S FOR YOU.

209
00:13:13,700 --> 00:13:14,966
- THIS IS BRANDON.

210
00:13:26,500 --> 00:13:28,600
- WHAT A STUPID THING TO DO.

211
00:13:29,566 --> 00:13:30,533
BRAT!

212
00:13:31,733 --> 00:13:32,866
IDIOT...

213
00:13:36,233 --> 00:13:38,100
- HUH?
- Sid: WHERE'S EDDIE?

214
00:13:38,166 --> 00:13:39,900
- WHAT'S GOING ON OLD MAN?

215
00:13:39,966 --> 00:13:42,366
- ( groaning in pain )

216
00:13:42,433 --> 00:13:45,000
- I ASKED YOU WHERE EDDIE IS,
NOW ANSWER ME.

217
00:13:45,066 --> 00:13:47,133
- HE'S IN THE BACK, SIR!

218
00:13:47,200 --> 00:13:49,366
- ( door opening )

219
00:13:49,433 --> 00:13:52,133
- HUH, OH, HI!
WHAT'S UP DAD?

220
00:13:52,200 --> 00:13:53,733
HEY WAIT TILL YOU HEAR THIS.

221
00:13:53,800 --> 00:13:56,033
I GOT A TIP THAT ALGERIA
PULLED UP A BIG HEIST

222
00:13:56,100 --> 00:13:59,000
AND EVERYTHING THEY
GOT IS OURS NOW.

223
00:13:59,066 --> 00:14:01,533
( groaning in pain )

224
00:14:01,600 --> 00:14:04,500
- YOU STUPID IDIOT!
- HUH, WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

225
00:14:04,566 --> 00:14:06,700
THIS JOB CAME OFF
WITHOUT A HITCH.

226
00:14:06,766 --> 00:14:09,733
AND ALL WITNESSES ARE DEAD,
YOU SHOULD BE THANKING ME.

227
00:14:09,800 --> 00:14:11,100
( groaning in pain )

228
00:14:11,166 --> 00:14:13,133
- YOU ACTED WITHOUT PERMISSION!

229
00:14:13,200 --> 00:14:16,000
- I'M NOT ALLOWED TO DO
ANYTHING ON MY OWN.

